Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.38,0:00:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.12,0:00:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜  小鸠鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.73,0:00:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见  星期一再见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.48,0:00:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.48,0:00:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙每次都这样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.51,0:00:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.70,0:00:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  快让开  要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.76,0:00:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要去打工吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.02,0:00:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小鸠  辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.55,0:00:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问有没有什么我可以帮忙的？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.18,0:00:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事了  你可以回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:00:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}打工招聘情报
