Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:35.80,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,140)\fad(950,1050)}「…侦探  花户小鸠。」
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------------------TEXT--------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.16,0:02:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工原来有这么多种啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.84,0:02:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借这种书回来打算做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.29,0:02:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是去打工啦  像藤本先生一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.26,0:02:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想帮忙还点债务吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.38,0:02:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.70,0:02:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在清爽的早晨发发报纸什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.99,0:02:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你这个老睡过头的家伙来干？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给大家送送披萨什么的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.44,0:03:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙绝对会迷路的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.92,0:03:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.49,0:03:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮忙搬家什么的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.11,0:03:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜你会脚下一滑把瓶瓶罐罐全摔碎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.02,0:03:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那打什么工才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.84,0:03:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要问我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.10,0:03:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是的  我不干了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.59,0:03:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猪尾吕义先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.55,0:03:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.58,0:03:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  破掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.51,0:03:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.11,0:03:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.07,0:03:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  缝好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.14,0:03:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有一件事情想拜托您
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.45,0:04:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.92,0:04:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔！借伞给我的先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.90,0:04:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  那时的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前段时间承蒙您的照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.26,0:04:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  你们已经认识啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.73,0:04:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  重新自我介绍一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.20,0:04:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是店长植田
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.57,0:04:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫花户小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.24,0:04:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠是我公寓里的房客
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常在艾草托儿所里帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.38,0:04:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说她在找打工的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.19,0:04:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是我就想到这家店了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只在店里很忙的周末来我们这里就已经帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的手痊愈之前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.54,0:04:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手弄成了这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.02,0:04:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么弄成这样的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.71,0:04:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我相当笨手笨脚的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.40,0:04:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是前段时间受的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.65,0:04:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.48,0:04:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但是忙的时候店长很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.18,0:05:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教  小鸠小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.53,0:05:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  请多指教  店长先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.10,0:05:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.32,0:05:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫大村裕美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.25,0:05:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教  小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.57,0:05:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么加油吧  小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.81,0:05:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我换好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.31,0:05:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  制服很合身呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.32,0:05:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么要做些什么好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.17,0:05:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…首先客人来的时候要说「欢迎光临」吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.95,0:05:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就…就是这种感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.34,0:05:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.15,0:05:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有就是当听到客人点餐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.70,0:05:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把蛋糕装进那个盒子里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.17,0:05:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.52,0:05:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帐由我来算  然后你收帐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说「多谢惠顾」是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.21,0:05:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.09,0:05:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.30,0:05:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:06:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那先试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.18,0:06:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…奶油蛋糕和蒙布朗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.54,0:06:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.86,0:06:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶油蛋糕和蒙布朗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.93,0:06:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}起司蛋糕…啊不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.05,0:06:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}苹果派…还有柠檬蛋挞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.03,0:06:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起司蛋糕…苹果派…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.29,0:06:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柠檬？呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.60,0:06:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要一个泡芙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.46,0:06:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.32,0:06:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶油蛋糕和蒙布朗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.29,0:06:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苹果派  柠檬蛋挞和泡芙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.26,0:06:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好厉害啊  裕美小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.04,0:06:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠  把这些装进盒子里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.80,0:06:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…奶油蛋糕和…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.86,0:06:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镇静些  换一块吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.87,0:06:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠  没问题吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.52,0:06:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.85,0:06:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有蒙布朗和…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.84,0:06:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苹果派  柠檬蛋挞和泡芙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.78,0:07:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.89,0:07:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  最后…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.61,0:07:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  充满活力的店员小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就可以了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.15,0:07:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  习惯之后就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.62,0:07:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  小鸠鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.59,0:07:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满里奈和你妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.87,0:07:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.88,0:07:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠鸠是蛋糕店员工啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.32,0:07:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  今天是蛋糕店员工
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.94,0:07:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.01,0:07:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要买什么蛋糕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.84,0:07:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是来拿满里奈的生日蛋糕的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.47,0:07:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  今天是你的生日啊  生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠  帮忙包起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.41,0:07:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.34,0:07:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.25,0:07:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.89,0:07:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.47,0:08:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  小鸠鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.23,0:08:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.14,0:08:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.90,0:08:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.52,0:08:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}（满里奈  生日快乐）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.27,0:08:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.12,0:08:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和别的搞错了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.72,0:08:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去追满里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.47,0:08:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.14,0:08:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠鸠  没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.44,0:08:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.81,0:08:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.45,0:08:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后请给我这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.54,0:08:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠  那边的客人要的是蒙布朗和起司蛋糕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.39,0:08:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.16,0:08:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.32,0:08:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.31,0:09:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您  猪尾吕义先生会很开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.09,0:09:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依哦…？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.94,0:09:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在别人面前是只布娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.22,0:09:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天也请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.81,0:09:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天也可以来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.37,0:09:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  当然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.24,0:09:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕美也可以回去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.72,0:09:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  但是  还没收拾好…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.64,0:09:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会做的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.51,0:09:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的伤还没有好  不要勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.81,0:09:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…店长我先…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.92,0:09:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.51,0:09:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不  没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.28,0:09:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是裕美小姐好像在担心什么的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.79,0:09:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很在意店长…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长先生吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像在烦恼什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我试着问过他一次  可他说没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.61,0:10:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.33,0:10:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店里生意也很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.48,0:10:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那店长先生在烦恼什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是债务吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.92,0:10:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾草托儿所因为那个弄得很麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.96,0:10:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠  莫非是为此才来我们这里打工的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.28,0:10:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.05,0:10:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了不起呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.47,0:10:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  比起我来  清花老师和藤本先生要了不起得多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想尽自己所能帮上他们的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.01,0:10:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想帮上…店长的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.38,0:10:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个相当美味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.76,0:10:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想帮忙却帮不上忙  很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.62,0:11:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去调查一下店长先生的烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.57,0:11:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  你要去也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.37,0:11:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可别因为多管闲事而被炒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.84,0:11:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就吃不到这美味的蛋糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.48,0:11:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  但是去各种地方打工也可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寿司店
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.98,0:11:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛排店
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高级中餐店
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.30,0:11:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠  下次去哪里打工？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.64,0:11:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还要在蛋糕店打工呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.45,0:11:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.06,0:11:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.97,0:11:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  可以帮我把这个曲奇摆到柜橱里么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.20,0:11:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.86,0:11:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.55,0:11:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才店长是不是看着我  然后叹了口气？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.05,0:11:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.30,0:12:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢  店长的烦恼和我有关吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去问问店长先生的烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.13,0:12:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.56,0:12:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗  那…能装作不经意帮我问一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.98,0:12:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  小鸠会加油的
Comment: 0,0:02:39.84,0:02:42.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.05,0:12:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.82,0:12:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.66,0:12:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.79,0:12:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实有件事想装作不经意地问一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.84,0:12:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.13,0:13:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.35,0:13:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长先生是不是有什么烦恼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.57,0:13:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系哦  什么事都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是裕美说了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.35,0:13:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时不时会想些什么  好像有什么话想说的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,样子很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.01,0:13:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什么值得裕美去在意的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.85,0:13:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.01,0:13:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样说的话反而更令人在意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.86,0:13:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.07,0:13:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  小鸠？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.13,0:13:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.67,0:13:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的伤痊愈之前请她在这里帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.47,0:13:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.16,0:13:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来买蛋糕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.84,0:13:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去千岁那里玩  想买点礼物去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.15,0:13:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没吃过了呢  奇洛儿的蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.26,0:13:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得您订做过丈夫的生日蛋糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:13:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老师的丈夫是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.86,0:14:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说结过婚有了老公吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.40,0:14:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我没见过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也许是离了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.12,0:14:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老师很寂寞的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.54,0:14:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事别直接去问哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.68,0:14:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.02,0:14:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人人都有不想说的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.16,0:14:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也没说是为了托儿所而打工么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人会把所有事情都讲出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.54,0:14:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇洛儿的店长先生也是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.48,0:14:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是裕美很想知道  这种时候该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄地调查什么的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.85,0:14:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我觉得这份差事不适合土鸠来做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.40,0:15:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.26,0:15:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的确是悄悄地…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.98,0:15:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小鸠姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.35,0:15:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在悄悄地调查
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.61,0:15:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.09,0:15:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像侦探一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.38,0:15:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侦探？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.97,0:15:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是侦探吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.14,0:15:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.79,0:15:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.18,0:15:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要调查很多东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.22,0:15:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动机什么的  不在场证明什么的  证据什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要搜查  取证  跟踪什么的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.15,0:15:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.20,0:15:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.16,0:15:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  侦探是一个人行动的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.33,0:15:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像往错误的方向去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.56,0:15:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.97,0:16:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我今天是侦探
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.01,0:16:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侦探？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.45,0:16:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇洛儿里有没有什么奇怪的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.06,0:16:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.47,0:16:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  发生了什么案件吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.63,0:16:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  店长先生在烦恼着这样的案件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.17,0:16:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.63,0:16:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在烦恼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么头绪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  就算问我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.36,0:16:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.72,0:16:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇洛儿的蛋糕很受欢迎  是工作之外的烦恼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.28,0:16:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.45,0:16:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.66,0:16:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那我们先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.14,0:16:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样我可看不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.21,0:16:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去动用我的调查网
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.80,0:16:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调查网？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.93,0:16:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.63,0:16:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情谁会接受
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.47,0:16:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真小气呢  玄琥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.35,0:16:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱咨询还是去找别处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.29,0:16:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那今天就拿着礼物回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.84,0:17:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙只是来我这里吃年轮蛋糕的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很懂事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.90,0:17:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.77,0:17:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.56,0:17:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.94,0:17:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕美
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.02,0:17:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.35,0:17:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.35,0:17:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.59,0:17:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做侦探
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.19,0:17:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到现在为止我知道的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇洛儿的蛋糕很受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.79,0:17:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦恼会不会是工作之外的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.29,0:17:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还知道了店长先生一直送小孩子巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.06,0:17:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还很关心别人的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.44,0:17:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很喜欢这样的店长先生做的蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.04,0:17:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后还收到了巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.09,0:17:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长对大家都很温柔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.74,0:17:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕美  下面要开始跟踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.11,0:18:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠  还是算了  回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.95,0:18:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.59,0:18:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约好了和谁见面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.34,0:18:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样跟在别人后面是不好的  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.97,0:18:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.27,0:18:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.71,0:18:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不认识的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.70,0:18:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不认识
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是约会  所以才没对我说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.83,0:18:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办  小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.54,0:18:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请冷静点  裕美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.43,0:18:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被店长发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕美？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.35,0:18:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.02,0:19:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.23,0:19:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.62,0:19:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.09,0:19:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.28,0:19:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.06,0:19:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个  刚才和店长先生见面的人是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.82,0:19:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是面试
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.07,0:19:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要来打工的新人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.93,0:19:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工…  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.99,0:19:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然周末小鸠能来  但一直没能给裕美放假
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放假？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.48,0:19:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你会不会累了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.37,0:19:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有受伤是不是也是因为这个原因
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.81,0:19:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长…  那你是因为这件事而烦恼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.72,0:19:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  裕美工作真的很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.80,0:19:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就这样把工作全交给你  真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.23,0:20:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会  我和店长一起工作很开心  所以不休息也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.82,0:20:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天接待因奇洛儿的蛋糕而高兴的客人们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.96,0:20:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能见到店长  这些都很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…  受伤是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.08,0:20:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.97,0:20:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是裕美做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.46,0:20:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  满手受伤是因为在练习做蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.86,0:20:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕是一点也好  我想要帮上店长的忙才学的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.92,0:20:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  一直瞒着你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.16,0:20:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以尝尝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.52,0:20:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…  可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.14,0:21:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.45,0:21:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.28,0:21:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工的新人也会来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.40,0:21:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后抽些时间一起来学习做蛋糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.67,0:21:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.43,0:21:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  已经解决了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.92,0:21:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  小鸠侦探解决了案件
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.57,0:21:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长先生想给裕美放假
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.93,0:21:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕美想想更多地帮助店长先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.00,0:21:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人相互为对方着想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.59,0:21:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样非常棒的案件
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.68,0:21:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  也好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.61,0:21:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也吃到了年轮蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.52,0:21:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个年轮蛋糕不是奇洛儿的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.07,0:21:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且以前也作为礼物带回来过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:21:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和猪尾吕义先生的调查网有什么关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.00,0:22:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了  这次的分数呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.99,0:22:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为吃到了蛋糕  出血大奉送  100分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.19,0:22:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.33,0:22:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.39,0:22:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.13,0:22:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.11,0:22:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我打工的店里的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.45,0:22:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工？  你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.91,0:22:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.39,0:22:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以藤本先生请稍微休息一下去大学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.39,0:22:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  你一加油就没什么好事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.87,0:22:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺负人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.96,0:22:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.59,0:22:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太勉强累倒了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.26,0:22:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非你是在担心我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.67,0:22:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.50,0:22:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.09,0:22:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说这个了  快把你脸上的涂鸦处理掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.64,0:22:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是100分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.91,0:22:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么啊  是涂鸦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.98,0:22:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  藤本先生欺负人所以50分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.62,0:22:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知所谓
